{"type": "article", "id": 32527, "title": "Line 和欧舒丹合作礼盒，以及，Gucci再次发布奇幻之旅 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-09-23T02:46:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 239, "name": "米兰时装周"}, {"id": 253, "name": "LINE"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 2040, "name": "KENZO"}, {"id": 2041, "name": "Jimmy Choo"}, {"id": 3289, "name": "梅西百货"}, {"id": 5910, "name": "Stuart Weitzman"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 33079, "name": "e.l.f"}, {"id": 33080, "name": "Odd Future"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/201609230919526DOgyMK7bm9eJhIt.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2016/09/elf-cosmetics-ipo-public-company\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国平价化妆品牌 e.l.f 在美国上市</b></a> | e.l.f 受千禧一代年轻消费者追捧，大部分产品售价在 1 美元到 30 美元之间。周四，它在美国上市，首日涨幅达 40%。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/macys-teams-up-with-grooming-services-provider-in-beauty-bush\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>梅西百货与 beGlammed 联手提供新娘装扮业务</b></a> | 为了挽救不断下滑的业绩，梅西百货与 beGlammed 联手推出了上门为新娘化妆的业务。beGlammed 是成立于 2014 年，提供的新娘妆服务业务的公司，其服务价格在 25 至 185 美元。此次与梅西合作，这项业务将被引入美国的 22 座城市。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/human-resources/paula-schneider-to-exit-american-apparel-ceo-post-10558846/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>American Apparel 的 CEO 将要离职</b></a> | 作为 American Apparel 的 CEO，Paula Schneider 将于 10 月 3 日正式离职。 American Apparel 的行政主管  Chelsea Grayson 将接任。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2016/business/retail/jimmy-choo-womens-store-milan-sandra-choi-260022-260022/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Jimmy Choo 的米兰精品店内正式推出定制服务</b></a> | 翻新后的 Jimmy Choo 米兰精品店，将推出私人定制和专属购物间服务。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/adidas-originals-x-italia-independent-sunglasses\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas Originals 与 Italia Independent 联手推出了一个限量版的太阳眼镜系列</a>。这个系列的灵感来自 80 年代的太阳镜的经典款式，包括了 4 款单品。前两款圆形镜框的墨镜更是用蓝色的三叶草 logo 把整个镜片一分为二，创意十足。该系列的墨镜每款限量 500 副，定价为 200 美元。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092708gCNixolJQ4cf5nIz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092718qbrgVtF826SweEjP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092726TYs9hlvPKZo2wD4k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092734cqEPvxIksTVitOZo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092744P94gAEv6hTGzULxI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>来看人气过膝靴<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/stuart-weitzman-boots-fall-2016-neiman-marcus/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Stuart Weitzman 的 2016 秋冬季新品宣传大片</a>。这组大片由超模 Valery Kaufman 和 Kelly Gale 共同演绎。展示了   Stuart Weitzman 经典的过膝长靴、高跟单鞋、及踝靴等多种鞋款。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092757caKSZNxY1sQT29ly.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092758r0kYcdFxKa3TCvDj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092758gBwhNDQH9oJxCVOU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092758vti7KhO1LDrbdfYj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092758OhFlmktjq2SP6baC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092758GVeYDxzWoEt8Af45.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092809xhtMlYFCvguPieIX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>日本的 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/beauty/skincare/line-friends-x-loccitane/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">Line Friends 再度与欧舒丹联手推出限定款礼盒套装</a>。欧舒丹经典产品 Shea Butter 换上了以星空为主题的深蓝色 Line Friends 卡通人物包装。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092820hGBE5uXgse1MW48A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092830BqoEZLtuCvmeai19.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092830cVMDyOv7ZsETtj9I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/kenzo-x-hm-campaign-chance-the-rapper-iman-suboi\" rel=\"nofollow\">KENZO 与 H&amp;M 合作</a>发布官方宣传照。由美国说唱歌手 Chance the Rapper、超模 Iman 与越南创作型女歌手 Suboi 联合演绎。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092901Np2c4bRZEAXGlPza.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092901BmeufAaoCv8YDyrl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092901feudDSqpHsQ2BK0m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>米兰时装周上，<a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/runway-fashion/mfw-gucci-spring-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gucci 的 2017 春夏系列</a>再一次带领观众走进了名为 Magic Lanterns 的奇幻旅程。整个系列新作以浪漫的荷叶边、丰富的色彩以及华丽的刺绣，延续了 Gucci 的复古浪漫。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092913KgyZtzWM9xiL5bIe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092913yrwBeEml14K0LOiM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092913dxmK4T9hSCreGN6U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092913Cr2VPmNbiBSplkKq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092913KsEHGymNnogzaD01.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609230929132sEdu4cf1BVv98rQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092914Lt9Th2aNrDdSJQAk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609230929145opDrL4qXyYOVCgT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092914Wl9TB5vDUekwdmE3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>人气嘻哈团体<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/odd-future-x-vans-sk8-hi-authentic\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Odd Future 与 Vans 合作推出新品</a>。该系列包括了 Sk8-Hi 和 Authentic 两个经典鞋型，以青绿色为底色，加上粉色黄色结合的 Odd Future 的标志性甜甜圈图案，打造青春时尚的感觉。定价分别为 65 和 52 英镑，将于 9 月 24 日正式开售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092924BJxYy3SvXrfKdsgz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160923092924hCBEnfl5dIZMPaiW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">&nbsp;</p>"}